<body>
<!-- this is a comment in HTML -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1>Rate {{courseName}}!</h1>
            <p>Rating courses is the best way to help out your fellow students and in turn yourself!!</p>
        </div>

        <p><center><b>So tell us how you REALLY feel!</b></center></p>
        <p><center><b>From 0 being least and 9 being greatest...</b></center></p>
        <br>

        <div class="col-xs-4">
            <p>Difficulty?</p>
            <select class="selectpicker" id=difficulty">
                <option>0</option>
                <option>1</option>
                <option>2</option>
